(227, 'Rotator cuff External rotators Eccentrics (90)', 'exercise', '{\"0\":\"               \",\"1\":\"                             \",\"2\":\"           \",\"3\":\"              ,   -  \",\"4\":\"          \"}', '{\"0\":\"Tie a resistance band somewhere at your chest level. Stand facing the band.\",\"1\":\"Hold the band in the exercising hand and lift it up sideways till shoulder level with the elbow bent halfway and wrist pointing towards the ceiling.\",\"2\":\"Maintaining the position walk behind to generate tension in the band.\",\"3\":\"Hold this position and in a controlled fashion let your arm rotate downwards, thus reducing the tension slowly.\",\"4\":\"Walk back towards the band to start the next repetition.\"}', NULL, 1, '2022-07-10 11:10:44', '2022-07-10 11:10:44'),
